    <note type="biography">
        <p>Russian jewellery manufacturers. Founded in Moscow by Pavel Fedorovich Sazikov in 1793. Court manufacturer of silver products. Exhibited at Russian and World Fairs, starting with London, 1851. The firm was acquired by Ivan Khlebnikov firm in 1887.</p>
